{"tid":1218564,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新加坡口香糖禁令","createTime":"2019-06-13T16:08:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T01:11:33.000Z","uid":64702,"like":879,"dislike":80,"uniUserReply":107,"replies":[{"pid":"693052da1404ade187f08938588ec8cf41130b5f","tid":1218564,"uid":64702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T16:08:21.000Z","msg":"新加坡地鐵和禁令的實施<br />\n1987年，耗資50億新元建造的新加坡地鐵投入使用。這在當時是新加坡實行的最大公共項目。後來據報道，<span style=\"color: red;\">一些破壞者把吃剩的口香糖粘在地鐵車門的傳感器上，使車門無法正常運作，影響到地鐵服務。</span>雖然此現象非常少見，但維護需要極高的費用，也很難抓到破壞者。1992年，剛接任新加坡總理的吳作棟決定發佈口香糖禁令。這一禁令隨《製造控制法》頒佈，此法律同時限定某些煙酒產品的銷售。[3]<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%96%B0%E5%8A%A0%E5%9D%A1%E5%8F%A3%E9%A6%99%E7%B3%96%E7%A6%81%E4%BB%A4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%258A%25A0%25E5%259D%25A1%25E5%258F%25A3%25E9%25A6%2599%25E7%25B3%2596%25E7%25A6%2581%25E4%25BB%25A4&d=BIOOYiAB7dh8oRe%2BrusdWd%2FmPfBwacFXLzUp2rw9Z8Q%3D&h=eabb434e\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%96%B0%E5%8A%A0%E5%9D%A1%E5%8F%A3%E9%A6%99%E7%B3%96%E7%A6%81%E4%BB%A4</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">大家記住唔好學啊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"129c4440dc3ea87480411a3067c81d79d510841e","tid":1218564,"uid":64702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T16:08:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cfccd085b9d4cd4947bb44bfe0da89441a1ea62b","tid":1218564,"uid":64702,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T16:08:47.000Z","msg":"推推"},{"pid":"b0143e06c7c7d39f93b267fa9850c5cd83a31fd0","tid":1218564,"uid":64702,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T16:08:58.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"0bde47617e63f314d0cecfbbacaea80a690f10cd","tid":1218564,"uid":64702,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T16:09:18.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"7ef9f2b0d0060106008e6d7258d33fe2629e18f3","tid":1218564