kgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T16:12:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df6107d8475c9b4fa5e7db3032a4c0e2c6ee9daa","tid":1218564,"uid":64702,"like":78,"dislike":0,"score":78,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T16:13:31.000Z","msg":"新加坡前總理李光耀在他的回憶錄中寫道，1983年時任國家發展部部長向他提出了禁止口香糖流通的建議。<span style=\"color: red;\">破壞者把嚼過的口香糖隨地亂吐，吐在郵箱、鑰匙孔和電梯按鈕上，引發建屋局組屋的維護不便。公共場所的地面、樓梯和行人路上的殘渣大大提高了清潔衛生的成本。</span>部長認為公共汽車上的口香糖殘渣同樣是個問題。但李光耀當時認為，實行這樣的禁令過於「嚴苛」。"},{"pid":"c2f92ba3ef1895986f1363b19a874ca224f8c6d5","tid":1218564,"uid":24714,"like":153,"dislike":0,"score":153,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T16:14:35.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<br />\n咁都得<br />\n香港人千祈唔好模仿"},{"pid":"6670c431f15e1bcc99442a5391f855afddcb0130","tid":1218564,"uid":64702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T16:14:38.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"67f0967bd62130f4ce062e1ebf08885c4775855b","tid":1218564,"uid":64702,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c2f92ba3ef1895986f1363b19a874ca224f8c6d5","tid":1218564,"uid":24714,"like":153,"dislike":0,"score":153,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T16:14:35.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<br />\n咁都得<br />\n香港人千祈唔好模仿"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T16:15:00.000Z","msg":"真係唔好學<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3af1fa83a3010026ab3dcbcef7b36d8a933848ac","tid":1218564,"uid":129340,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T16:15:57.000Z","msg":"唔好學"},{"pid":"9ae384a13577ef8c95ab60818ceb5434ae474b61","tid":1218564,"uid":64702,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T16:16:00.000Z","msg":"推，唔好學啊大家"},{"pid":"9241c2aba0b9c0b60edccc8082a39e5e82d513a9","tid":1218564,"uid":49697,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T16:16:07.000Z","msg":"強烈要求置頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/