6:08:21.000Z","msg":"新加坡地鐵和禁令的實施<br />\n1987年，耗資50億新元建造的新加坡地鐵投入使用。這在當時是新加坡實行的最大公共項目。後來據報道，<span style=\"color: red;\">一些破壞者把吃剩的口香糖粘在地鐵車門的傳感器上，使車門無法正常運作，影響到地鐵服務。</span>雖然此現象非常少見，但維護需要極高的費用，也很難抓到破壞者。1992年，剛接任新加坡總理的吳作棟決定發佈口香糖禁令。這一禁令隨《製造控制法》頒佈，此法律同時限定某些煙酒產品的銷售。[3]<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%96%B0%E5%8A%A0%E5%9D%A1%E5%8F%A3%E9%A6%99%E7%B3%96%E7%A6%81%E4%BB%A4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%258A%25A0%25E5%259D%25A1%25E5%258F%25A3%25E9%25A6%2599%25E7%25B3%2596%25E7%25A6%2581%25E4%25BB%25A4&d=BIOOYiAB7dh8oRe%2BrusdWd%2FmPfBwacFXLzUp2rw9Z8Q%3D&h=eabb434e\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%96%B0%E5%8A%A0%E5%9D%A1%E5%8F%A3%E9%A6%99%E7%B3%96%E7%A6%81%E4%BB%A4</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">大家記住唔好學啊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T17:37:24.000Z","msg":"唔洗香口膠，用張紙仔都得<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利：有次搭mtr lift見佢lift長響，入去就知原來個感應器遮左先閂唔到<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n真心同你地講唔好唔好唔好玩門"},{"pid":"94c0c353cf7d20a98d58fddcc14f775aa4a85761","tid":1218564,"uid":9906,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ccbc98c5a1b84d66e02a661c5a61d1ceb09c96a4","tid":1218564,"uid":103759,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T16:50:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>有口水/指紋 查DNA同CCTV會查到 </strong></span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T17:37:54.000Z","msg":"捉一個都唔知要用幾多人力物力時間金錢，不過都係果句啦，唔好學"},{"pid":"22fbddd4e86c22fb2315e34539a155930638e5fc","tid":1218564,"uid":64702,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"50940df67820f4ad690d0c218da853f6a2d81829","tid":1218564,"uid":17392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T17:23:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/91qHzho.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F91qHzho.png&h=2b33