\">一些破壞者把吃剩的口香糖粘在地鐵車門的傳感器上，使車門無法正常運作，影響到地鐵服務。</span>雖然此現象非常少見，但維護需要極高的費用，也很難抓到破壞者。1992年，剛接任新加坡總理的吳作棟決定發佈口香糖禁令。這一禁令隨《製造控制法》頒佈，此法律同時限定某些煙酒產品的銷售。[3]<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%96%B0%E5%8A%A0%E5%9D%A1%E5%8F%A3%E9%A6%99%E7%B3%96%E7%A6%81%E4%BB%A4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%258A%25A0%25E5%259D%25A1%25E5%258F%25A3%25E9%25A6%2599%25E7%25B3%2596%25E7%25A6%2581%25E4%25BB%25A4&d=BIOOYiAB7dh8oRe%2BrusdWd%2FmPfBwacFXLzUp2rw9Z8Q%3D&h=eabb434e\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%96%B0%E5%8A%A0%E5%9D%A1%E5%8F%A3%E9%A6%99%E7%B3%96%E7%A6%81%E4%BB%A4</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">大家記住唔好學啊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T17:54:57.000Z","msg":"喂喂喂 起碼星期日之後先發夢啦<br />\n而家全世界都撐我地 咪學高官自己做7野"},{"pid":"6a8afbc9af9950a0b3f2c57951d3b6ec40787692","tid":1218564,"uid":199689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T17:56:34.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bf2df6344487ded451bd67d7cb047c1466b7847","tid":1218564,"uid":237962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T17:59:14.000Z","msg":"食過嘅香口膠會有唾液"},{"pid":"75461865f9d5c491cf843ec77c51d70b771b14db","tid":1218564,"uid":172465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T18:00:40.000Z","msg":"極權國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e6b5f4df17b220358658352742d80f9705ad6b9","tid":1218564,"uid":16976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T18:07:05.000Z","msg":"DNA<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef474291e9c8d6ff877412a3b9c46263075eec48","tid":1218564,"uid":34604,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T18:08:23.000Z","msg":"［真心唔好玩野］唔好再搞地鐵，你想搞既 入一入黎先<br />\n<a href=\"https://li